data.name: Product Details - Returns detailed information for a product and similar products

data.description: Lists all brands, along with their IDs, matching query term. Does not support wildcards. Limit is 10 results per query.

response.name: Search Brands - Lists all brands along with their IDs Model

data.name: Search Brands - Lists all brands along with their IDs
brandId
data.description: Limits results to products of brand with id int. Supports multiple, comma-separated values (acts as OR operator

data.name: categoryId
data.description: Limits results to products of category with this id

data.name: endPrice
data.description: Combined with start_price, limits results to products sold by at least one store at a price between start and end

data.name: pageNumber
data.description: The page number of the result set to return. 10 results per page, plus similar items.

data.name: query
data.description: The product search term - could be either product title, SKU, UPC or MPN. To search by SKU input 'sku:<value>'. For UPC search, input 'upc:<value>'.

data.name: sortBy
data.description: Sort by values - RELEVANCE, PRICE_LOW_TO_HIGH, PRICE_HIGH_TO_LOW, MOST_RECENT

data.name: startPrice
data.description: Combined with end_price, limits results to products sold by at least one store at a price between start and end

data.name: storeId
data.description: Limits results to products sold at store with id int. Supports multiple, comma-separated values (acts as OR operator)
Returns a collection of products matching a specified query, along with a variety of statistics about the query results. Requires at least one of query, brandId, storeId, or categoryId.
